title: some calendars do not sync anymore
body:
### expected behaviour
sync all calendars

### actual behaviour
only one calendar syncs

### steps to reproduce
1. not applicable


### server configuration
operating system: centos 6.5

web server: apache 2.2.3

database: mysql 5

php version: 5.3

owncloud version: 6 rc4

### client configuration
browser: ff

operating system: linux
